it.polimi.se2019.View.GUI

Class Map3UIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.View.GUI.Map3UIController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class Map3UIController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Controller class that manages the main user interface. It parses the data received by the network and loads the graphic resources neededs. In order to send an answer, there are methods with specific purposes assigned to the graphic elements.
